/08BIZ-TECHTIP-TOPART/08BIZ-TECHTIP-TOPART-videoSixteenByNineJumbo1600.jpg" medium="image"><media:credit>Google; Samsung; Apple</media:credit><media:description>From left, the Google Health, the Samsung Health and Apple’s Health apps offer plenty of tools and features to help you manage your diet, exercise and personal safety.</media:description></media:content></item><item><title>The A.I. Trade Secrets War + Economists Say ‘We Must Act Now’ + HatGPT</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/17/podcasts/hardfork-ai-trade-secrets.html?partner=rss&amp;emc=rss</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/17/podcasts/hardfork-ai-trade-secrets.html?partner=rss&amp;emc=rss</guid><atom:link rel="standout" href="https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/17/podcasts/hardfork-ai-trade-secrets.html?partner=rss&amp;emc=rss" /><description>“I don’t know if the public understands this, but these companies hate each other.”</description><dc:creator>Kevin Roose, Casey Newton, Whitney Jones, Rachel Cohn, Vjeran Pavic, Alyssa Moxley, Dan Powell, Elisheba Ittoop, Rowan Niemisto and Diane Wong</dc:creator><pubDate>Fri, 17 Jul 2026 11:00:03 GMT</pubDate><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_des">science</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_des">OpenAI</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_des">Anthropic</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_des">Apple</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_des">Artificial intelligence</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_des">Lorde</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_des">internal-open-access-audio</category><media:content url="https://static01.nyt.com/images/2026/07/17/podcasts/17hardfork-AI-Wars/17hardfork-AI-Wars-videoSixteenByNineJumbo1600.png" medium="image"><media:credit>Photo Illustration